Remarks. Imported from Hawaii in 1921 in an
S . oleae
biocontrol program, this species was reported established in California (
Bartlett 1978 a
). It was not recovered in later surveys of
S . oleae
parasitoids (
Kennett 1986
;
Daane et al. 1991
;
Lampson & Morse 1992
), but was collected once in northern California in 1994 ( RLZC ).
